definition: eminent beyond or above comparison, a single person or thing
details:
adjective
- eminent beyond or above comparison
= synonyms: nonpareil
- indefinite in time or position
- used informally as an intensifier
- of the same kind or quality
- having the indivisible character of a unit
= synonyms: unitary
- being a single entity made by combining separate components
= example: being a single entity made by combining separate components
- used of a single unit or thing
= synonyms: i, ane
noun
- a single person or thing
= example: a single person or thing
- the smallest whole number or a numeral representing this number
= example: the smallest whole number or a numeral representing this number
= synonyms: single
